Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:25.60,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,1000)\pos(844,718)}对决！登山料理！?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次在山顶吃的三明治好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再做给我吃好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.31,0:00:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次要用登山装备做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有炉具和Kocher 什么都能做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs32}Kocher 德语 便携炊具
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.34,0:00:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,料理才没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.56,0:00:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我们来料理对决吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.32,0:00:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}又被日向牵着鼻子走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.90,0:00:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 Kocher是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是轻便炊具
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.93,0:00:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用它能做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要煮一下就能吃的美味料理…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把食材切好了 可肉类怎样办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好深奥啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉已经乐在其中了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前自娱自乐的时候都没这种感觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.94,0:00:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种心情… 是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.44,0:00:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是为了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 我一定赢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.51,0:01:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord3\3c&H000000&\an5\pos(1160,140)}虾仁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord3\3c&H000000&\an5\pos(1160,240)}鸡肉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord3\3c&H000000&\an5\pos(1160,350)}蛤蜊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.14,0:01:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord3\3c&H000000&\an5\pos(1160,450)}彩椒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\bord3\3c&H000000&\an5\pos(1160,550)}没淘过的米
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把事先处理好的食材放进锅里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.27,0:01:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入高汤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盖上铝膜 加热至水分蒸干
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火候好难掌握啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！ 我说你还做不做了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做 做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做超好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.45,0:01:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焖5分钟左右 加上柠檬…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.91,0:01:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海鲜烩饭出锅！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点糊了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超好吃！ 真不愧是小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不经意的一句「谢谢」也好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.98,0:01:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 一定是因为我很久没听到「谢谢」了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.64,0:01:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你的料理做好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.74,0:01:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 就在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.89,0:01:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘑菇酱通心粉… 好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:01:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺好吃的！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲜味很足 确实称得上一道料理！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明没看到你做啊 这是怎样做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎么能作弊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用脱水食材谁都能做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱水食材？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:17.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\fad(0,1000)}正\N宗\N \N鸡\N蛋\N鸡\N肉\N盖\N饭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.09,0:02:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,例如这个 包装里是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.21,0:02:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过放进碗里 加热水后…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向同学 麻烦你解释一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.72,0:02:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊 我不会做料理的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.56,0:02:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.46,0:02:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真对不起 让爸爸帮我做了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回是正式的 开动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那些没吃饱吧 所以让爸爸做了好多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道日向其实懂得照顾其他人的想法？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 吃东西的时候别说话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:02:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}行こう！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}スタッカートみたいに 胸を叩くワクワク感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}不思議　不安より
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}楽しみの容量が増えたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}また明日！やっほー
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.38,0:03:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}昂扬感像断奏音符般拍打胸膛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}真奇妙 不但没有不安
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}快乐的容量反而更大了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fs32\blur3\3c&H252527&}明天再见！YAHOO
